task.summary: -Implemented the tiny library service to be able to retrieve libraries based off criteria.
-Updated TinyLibrary Repo and Services for additional library retrieval to include books based off certain criteria.
- Updated TinyLibrary Services to be able to add/remove/update books for a provided ObjectID of a Tiny Library. - Added three new fields to Book/BookDTO for Author and quantity.
-Updated TinyLibraryDto to hold the a string value ID instead of ObjectID. -Added more PUT functions to handle a mass check in of books.
